{"type":"message","id":"fe7e7f16","parentId":"c89f4f03","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:12:58.271Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating heartbeat needs**\n\nI’m thinking about whether I need a heartbeat or watchdog for monitoring. Should I follow the startup read for the SOUL USER? Maybe I should look at today’s and yesterday’s memory, or even since the main session began. I’m wondering if the cron is isolated and if the current session is considered main. There seems to be a need for a system event response, possibly sending a HEARTBEAT_OK. I need to check HEARTBEAT.md and related files for more clarity.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0a4db9316dc248ac0169c2d4259a9081918b0a0d75b620718b\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpwtQq1tVDE5hTvAqyStPMbcgmVbTZlWYHiKmf4_aup1F2nnaI4-HsC4WGRiwwavg_Jox-K2HU7fdKuhPeAsgr92QorHHFi4Jk_SoQQtUhX1bwbJhZGIu5LFycttHCEaa95j0R894iQmAg7t0eMa-FPhr-tZqa_SfPnU2ViCaNjz54J6hcdGW4oKKaxVKFHZy-wCHBTSvFdKHy7bevUa1DZYObq7RJvwhl8HxrpDkABjiMV7MaphP7XR19Do34OPzHeKzazLK6OY2UTEDOsm35qVwlftC07v682_PfFkPaK0-Vdt2_buZSKn_s4D_ouv01VroqbO7vftOtJmpD5cAnvo_Koc74Z2oWPixu6rdYrrnSD1LCY2U96fLxmKVRpzJ2xO2dwA50NRK6Vks6VpYrCg4enoLV84TcFb1hz5ot1_tDKarYWW6hOlHzH7mN4OkTifmAK2J-wZp2gci98h-eBWtfgh7e_nQ4eYBLoEf46ekbLn6jSnY2rCOg968dwWrPVvK2sDtOfR0PRw9uhxzvjwBZwAMroVw1lN-22nBA_J45D9QWAC5zZWdr1s1qp3RL0Fn0vVikMggtG4vtGKpWOIfkPvgc-gce2iJZrO5ZTqnSmh2yml_iC8c4KlgjqoN5csEQFOVONVAF8awqMWRjwJ_s8kRHKUHEcpyRfRfsjKCrTp4S4usCQSpbVGBPRno8KDV6-405JQ84PcVCbardZ0WvyoIo73JqxeKVcqmBHgh9J5DJ1KNm3wLC2bs3enYwAHLSEDLcH1FUqaIT3T3DeP4MHxBYmj5-AcgxFwMVVZNp-ho27uXY7jqa1yShgrzacB3pNsNZInC6YqedkOCuo2m5loB1lDAt8HCMEznF_P9ik2Zf0x50Q9Xr6VGJdCDwiHYOTgql4wdvyOVyehEnlu7lPBBLgKcNypNmAha2259iIQYjO1Vm90gT6y201aWHI9HBPvx4oKL_Vn33SnjOrkQcWXFRI3iHdxDyxGDUf6sN44b1TDvStMg08kvoX6A2qcABniQ_atc3JeBC-DdILAvswRendMKci9tJMP02utJwhFKi6cSwNgDOA9J1HSHmOgr8TQSFtQmd68fUzpc82LVofwhmjZuAxPWAcWwgYQ1a4cImDEI6SKgx3XiF9QX7UdMljpyXIAYiFOLaJWOPjNvt5LZaEFVWBJsXgMc1pEZ7VRv8